WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 6]

01:48.200 --> 01:48.930
Back then,

01:50.280 --> 01:52.410
I severed my spiritual tail in one desperate gamble

01:53.920 --> 01:55.130
and nearly died.

01:56.070 --> 01:57.050
When I was at death's door,

01:57.590 --> 01:59.180
it was Master Dragon Deity who saved me.

02:01.150 --> 02:02.740
He granted me a portion

02:03.350 --> 02:04.770
of his own Dragon Deity's Power,

02:06.510 --> 02:07.820
and that's how I survived.

02:09.710 --> 02:10.690
So

02:12.030 --> 02:13.340
we made a pact.

02:14.310 --> 02:15.850
I lent out the nine-tailed power

02:18.000 --> 02:19.780
and swore to protect the Dragon Deity forever.

02:27.560 --> 02:28.820
And yet you still broke the pact.

02:30.120 --> 02:31.100
Yuan Wuhuo

02:31.400 --> 02:32.260
is truly vicious.

02:33.310 --> 02:34.170
He stirred up murders

02:34.360 --> 02:35.220
and panic,

02:35.710 --> 02:37.940
shook the people's faith in Master Dragon Deity,

02:38.630 --> 02:40.410
and used that chance to weaken his power.

02:41.120 --> 02:43.380
As the goodness in people's hearts is eroded

02:43.740 --> 02:44.660
and malice begins to grow,

02:45.090 --> 02:46.220
Jiu Ying's power

02:46.870 --> 02:48.170
grows stronger and stronger.

02:48.840 --> 02:49.940
When the Dragon Deity falls,

02:50.590 --> 02:52.060
Jiu Ying will break free of his seal

02:52.750 --> 02:54.060
and return to this world.

03:05.030 --> 03:05.890
You've been stalling us

03:06.630 --> 03:08.340
to buy time for those two.

03:09.120 --> 03:09.570
Wangyan,

03:10.240 --> 03:11.340
they're trying to take Xiaowei away.

03:15.400 --> 03:16.010
Shiguang,

03:16.470 --> 03:18.920
are you planning to snatch him by force?

03:20.310 --> 03:21.730
Now that you've seen through it,

03:23.000 --> 03:24.060
you're staying here,

03:24.310 --> 03:25.220
whether you want to or not.

03:26.910 --> 03:27.940
Under normal circumstances,

03:28.750 --> 03:29.920
if you wanted me to stay,

03:30.280 --> 03:31.290
I'd be more than happy to.

03:32.030 --> 03:33.200
But today,

03:33.680 --> 03:35.380
I'm afraid you won't be able to keep me.

04:14.470 --> 04:14.980
Wangyan,

04:15.360 --> 04:15.980
are you all right?

04:17.840 --> 04:18.570
I'm fine.

04:21.430 --> 04:22.700
You hurt my sister?

04:23.680 --> 04:25.400
I'll make you bleed too!

04:57.940 --> 05:01.700
[Golden Weave]

05:02.160 --> 05:02.610
Xiaowei,

05:03.750 --> 05:04.730
you broke your vow

05:05.360 --> 05:06.170
and took innocent lives.

05:07.040 --> 05:07.980
I'm taking you back

05:08.310 --> 05:09.580
to the Shilin Sect now to face judgment.

05:17.510 --> 05:19.420
The Dragon Deity's Power inside you

05:20.240 --> 05:22.050
can dispel all curses

05:22.720 --> 05:24.290
and bring the dead back to life.

05:24.720 --> 05:26.730
Use it to save Yu Shengwei.

05:27.310 --> 05:27.850
The butterfly demon.

05:28.510 --> 05:29.170
The butterfly demon?

05:40.120 --> 05:41.100
Save her.

05:41.720 --> 05:42.580
Save her.

05:43.430 --> 05:44.780
Bring Wang Sheng back.

05:46.040 --> 05:47.610
Don't you want to repay your debt?

05:49.950 --> 05:52.340
Only you can save her now.

06:08.040 --> 06:08.610
Stop!

06:22.240 --> 06:23.730
That butterfly demon is stealing the Dragon Deity's Power.

06:25.560 --> 06:26.170
Liu Weixue,

06:26.600 --> 06:27.250
stop!

07:24.270 --> 07:25.100
Dragon scales?

08:24.950 --> 08:26.050
I didn't expect

08:26.600 --> 08:29.140
there'd be a double-flower hunter here too.

09:29.840 --> 09:31.220
A double-flower hunter

09:31.390 --> 09:32.940
is as formidable as I thought.

10:07.320 --> 10:08.060
Ji Ling, come here!

10:48.480 --> 10:49.220
Ji Ling!

10:58.270 --> 10:58.650
Ji Ling!

10:58.790 --> 10:59.250
Back off!

11:06.720 --> 11:07.450
Ji...

11:40.390 --> 11:41.980
It seems he can no longer suppress the demon power inside him.

11:42.480 --> 11:43.430
He's about to lose control.

11:43.510 --> 11:44.610
That's not demon power.

12:15.950 --> 12:17.180
What happened to the Ice Curse?

12:18.480 --> 12:19.250
Why can he

12:19.320 --> 12:20.940
use his power so recklessly

12:21.320 --> 12:22.380
without being hunted?

12:22.380 --> 12:23.930
He's using the Dragon Deity's Power.

12:24.750 --> 12:26.420
Naturally, it won't trigger the Ice Curse.

12:27.270 --> 12:28.250
Dragon Deity's Power?

12:29.670 --> 12:31.380
How could Xiaowei have the Dragon Deity's Power?

12:34.480 --> 12:34.980
Commander Li.

12:39.120 --> 12:39.700
Ji Ling?

13:14.120 --> 13:14.770
Demon marks?

13:27.480 --> 13:27.940
Wangyan,

13:28.670 --> 13:30.060
Xiaowei's power is completely out of control.

13:30.440 --> 13:30.980
What do we do?

13:31.060 --> 13:32.770
Only the Dragon Deity can deal with him.

13:33.440 --> 13:34.850
But he's in the Shilin Sect.

13:35.360 --> 13:36.700
He'd never come to the Wei mansion for Xiaowei.

13:37.200 --> 13:38.580
Then we'll bring Xiaowei to the Dragon Deity.

13:39.360 --> 13:40.060
Hold him off.

13:40.840 --> 13:42.250
I'll take Ms. Yu to the Dragon Deity Temple.

14:22.480 --> 14:23.300
Master Dragon Deity,

14:24.510 --> 14:25.770
he was gravely wounded by Xiaowei,

14:26.910 --> 14:27.490
and now,

14:28.750 --> 14:29.370
he's beyond saving.

15:11.360 --> 15:12.250
Dispose of him.

15:14.150 --> 15:14.890
Yes.

16:16.320 --> 16:16.980
Out of the way!

16:19.120 --> 16:19.820
Out of the way!

16:22.080 --> 16:22.730
Out of the way!

16:43.030 --> 16:43.850
A barrier?

16:46.930 --> 16:47.770
Do you have a death wish?

16:48.200 --> 16:49.650
This barrier was set with the Dragon Deity's Power.

16:50.080 --> 16:50.850
It'll kill you!

16:52.150 --> 16:53.100
Give her back to me!

17:01.870 --> 17:02.460
Take her.

17:33.200 --> 17:34.010
That brat

17:35.640 --> 17:36.730
sure knows how to play dirty.

17:53.480 --> 17:54.460
Brilliant.

18:02.830 --> 18:03.490
The barrier

18:04.920 --> 18:05.840
has been broken.

18:07.440 --> 18:08.290
How could that happen?

18:11.240 --> 18:12.980
Xiaowei carries the Dragon Deity's Power.

18:14.350 --> 18:15.860
Naturally, he can destroy the barrier.

18:17.030 --> 18:17.570
Master,

18:18.480 --> 18:19.380
stay here.

18:20.110 --> 18:21.140
I'll deal with Xiaowei.

18:32.440 --> 18:33.090
Wu Shiguang!

18:56.790 --> 18:57.290
Don't be afraid.

18:58.550 --> 18:59.700
I'll bring you back right now.

19:15.200 --> 19:15.730
Wangyan,

19:16.830 --> 19:18.050
he's using the Dragon Deity's Power.

19:18.720 --> 19:19.290
Xiaowei,

19:19.640 --> 19:20.620
Ms. Yu's injuries are too severe.

19:20.640 --> 19:21.570
She can't be saved.

19:22.240 --> 19:23.600
Using the Dragon Deity's Power to forcibly

19:23.600 --> 19:24.300
reverse life and death

19:24.300 --> 19:25.290
goes against the laws of heaven.

19:26.270 --> 19:27.570
You'll be reduced to ashes too!

19:28.440 --> 19:29.380
I don't care!

19:31.350 --> 19:32.810
Well, I do.

19:43.550 --> 19:44.090
Wangyan.

19:50.640 --> 19:51.490
How dare you demons

19:52.480 --> 19:54.050
barge into the Dragon Deity Temple?

20:00.640 --> 20:01.140
Word Magic?

20:01.750 --> 20:02.420
Stay on guard.

20:08.350 --> 20:10.090
Piercing frost,

20:12.030 --> 20:13.810
let utter darkness descend.

20:34.280 --> 20:34.730
Why...

20:35.640 --> 20:36.620
why can't I see?

20:45.640 --> 20:46.380
Wangyan...

20:50.960 --> 20:51.960
Steady your mind.

20:52.240 --> 20:53.400
Don't let Xiaowei control you.

21:02.440 --> 21:03.620
Xiaowei's Word Magic

21:04.240 --> 21:05.120
really is formidable.

21:17.850 --> 21:19.630
Li Jie isn't affected?

21:20.480 --> 21:22.320
It seems Li Jie's physical cultivation

21:23.000 --> 21:23.970
is anything but ordinary.

21:24.510 --> 21:25.980
No wonder he could fight us blow for blow

21:26.640 --> 21:27.780
with nothing but that long blade,

21:28.110 --> 21:28.810
without relying

21:28.830 --> 21:29.810
on sacred power.

21:30.750 --> 21:32.220
That man is not to be taken lightly.

21:39.110 --> 21:40.260
We can't let him kill Xiaowei.

21:40.920 --> 21:41.940
Wuyi, let's go.

21:50.350 --> 21:51.020
As expected,

21:51.720 --> 21:53.060
the three foxes have joined forces.

22:11.350 --> 22:12.090
Wuyi!

22:47.270 --> 22:48.300
Eastern Purple Lightning,

22:48.680 --> 22:50.100
grant me your power.

23:26.110 --> 23:26.850
Wangyan!

24:16.720 --> 24:17.370
Wuyi.

24:17.960 --> 24:18.500
Wangyan,

24:19.110 --> 24:19.980
I'm fine.

24:28.960 --> 24:30.740
Greetings, Master Dragon Deity!

24:50.070 --> 24:51.060
The Dragon Deity?

24:52.240 --> 24:53.060
Wangyan,

24:53.880 --> 24:55.020
that wasn't the Dragon Deity's Power.

24:55.310 --> 24:56.480
It was the Eastern Purple Lightning

24:56.480 --> 24:57.410
from the high-rank demon Bai Ze.

24:57.830 --> 24:59.480
Bai Ze knows the weaknesses of all demons.

24:59.590 --> 25:00.650
Under

25:00.960 --> 25:02.410
the Eastern Purple Lightning,

25:02.920 --> 25:04.130
no demon can hide

25:04.680 --> 25:05.940
or escape pursuit.

25:08.110 --> 25:09.850
No wonder he didn't strike those demon hunters

25:10.000 --> 25:11.130
and only attacked us.

25:12.680 --> 25:14.130
Looks like the rumors were true.

25:19.110 --> 25:19.890
But

25:20.270 --> 25:21.780
why did he attack Wu Shiguang too?

25:39.270 --> 25:40.060
Xiaowei,

25:41.680 --> 25:43.060
you've committed a grave crime.

25:44.830 --> 25:45.780
I know.

25:47.160 --> 25:48.740
But I have to save her.

25:50.200 --> 25:53.090
The Dragon Deity's Power is meant to save all living beings.

25:54.240 --> 25:55.610
It cannot be used for one person alone.

25:58.680 --> 26:00.130
Having been granted the Dragon Deity's Power,

26:00.750 --> 26:01.890
I swear never to claim it for myself,

26:02.270 --> 26:03.460
never to use it for evil,

26:04.200 --> 26:05.740
but only to protect all living beings.

26:06.400 --> 26:07.700
If I break this oath,

26:08.030 --> 26:09.370
may I be shattered to pieces

26:09.720 --> 26:10.940
and doomed forever.

26:22.200 --> 26:23.610
Even if I'm shattered to pieces

26:24.440 --> 26:25.740
and doomed forever,

26:26.830 --> 26:28.570
I must save her.

27:45.960 --> 27:47.130
Stubborn fool.

27:52.750 --> 27:53.980
Everything you said by my bedside

27:54.830 --> 27:57.300
while I was unconscious...

27:58.960 --> 28:00.090
I heard it all.

28:01.830 --> 28:03.090
For hundreds of years,

28:05.190 --> 28:06.680
through life after life,

28:08.400 --> 28:10.410
all I've ever wanted was to keep you safe.

28:12.200 --> 28:13.090
But now,

28:14.700 --> 28:16.000
I've only hurt you.

28:20.870 --> 28:22.300
I never knew

28:22.920 --> 28:23.890
the chestnut cakes

28:25.110 --> 28:26.370
were made by you.

28:27.350 --> 28:28.740
I've felt

28:29.110 --> 28:30.330
your heart.

28:32.240 --> 28:34.740
Can you grant me one wish?

28:35.160 --> 28:36.330
Yes, of course.

28:37.030 --> 28:38.130
Whatever it takes,

28:38.590 --> 28:39.810
even if I'm torn apart,

28:40.480 --> 28:41.810
I'll keep my word.

28:44.240 --> 28:45.370
Let me...

28:47.240 --> 28:48.220
go.

28:50.240 --> 28:51.370
Use your power

28:52.200 --> 28:54.610
to save more people.

28:56.160 --> 28:58.370
The people of Luo'an

28:59.640 --> 29:00.670
are waiting for you.

29:00.670 --> 29:01.220
No...

29:01.840 --> 29:02.990
No!

29:02.990 --> 29:04.940
No...

29:05.310 --> 29:06.460
I don't want to!

29:08.640 --> 29:11.850
Grant me this final wish.

29:11.850 --> 29:12.410
No,

29:12.920 --> 29:13.850
I don't want to.

29:14.310 --> 29:15.220
No...

29:29.680 --> 29:31.060
Dragon hearts as one,

29:32.160 --> 29:33.500
all to source return,

29:39.830 --> 29:41.370
all barriers break.

29:42.940 --> 29:48.940
♪Some plant flowers, some burn joss paper♪

29:49.420 --> 29:55.700
♪In this mortal world, we've borrowed a hundred fleeting years...♪

29:56.720 --> 29:57.610
Th...

29:58.480 --> 29:59.780
thank you.

30:02.420 --> 30:08.020
♪You are like moonlight, leading me back home♪

30:08.500 --> 30:13.940
♪By the little window, I leave a few lines of ink♪

30:14.420 --> 30:20.180
♪One line writes of withering yellow, one line of forgiveness...♪

30:22.160 --> 30:23.460
You were nothing but a pawn.

30:23.460 --> 30:24.000
[Fourteenth year of the Zhenyuan era]

30:24.000 --> 30:25.370
Every word I ever said to you

30:26.000 --> 30:26.890
was a lie.

30:27.510 --> 30:28.500
But you refused to believe it.

30:29.160 --> 30:31.940
Your heart is filled with nothing but your own obsession.

30:33.960 --> 30:35.260
My heart has long belonged to the Buddha.

30:35.260 --> 30:36.160
[Twentieth year of the Shengjing era]

30:36.160 --> 30:37.220
I carry no more attachments.

30:38.510 --> 30:40.020
Let go of your obsession.

30:49.780 --> 30:52.540
[Nineteenth year of the Changyun era]

31:14.380 --> 31:19.580
♪You're moonlight, frost that burns bright♪

31:20.420 --> 31:25.860
♪Shining through my fearful flight...♪

31:29.000 --> 31:31.260
The Wang Sheng who gave his life to save you

31:31.270 --> 31:32.650
died long ago.

31:33.200 --> 31:35.130
You've been searching for him for hundreds of years,

31:35.750 --> 31:37.020
life after life.

31:37.960 --> 31:40.090
But we're not who you're looking for.

31:40.480 --> 31:42.060
You used your Formless Moon mark

31:42.440 --> 31:44.610
to mark them in the vast sea of people

31:45.110 --> 31:46.300
so you could find them.

31:46.960 --> 31:48.060
But in truth,

31:48.750 --> 31:51.090
they were all just strangers passing through your life.

31:56.480 --> 31:58.500
You said you were looking for Wang Sheng,

31:59.160 --> 32:00.700
that you wanted to repay his kindness.

32:02.310 --> 32:03.570
But really,

32:04.200 --> 32:05.310
you're only trapped

32:05.310 --> 32:07.700
by an obsession you refuse to let go of.

32:08.300 --> 32:13.420
♪The River of Oblivion in their eyes, their hearts the Fountain of Youth♪

32:14.260 --> 32:20.020
♪Stitch by stitch, the cuckoo's bloodstained wish is sewn♪

32:20.300 --> 32:25.740
♪The wind blows, the clouds scatter, and tears fall on a jade plate...♪

32:26.440 --> 32:27.500
Kites for sale!

32:27.880 --> 32:29.260
All kinds of kites!

32:30.550 --> 32:31.170
Miss,

32:31.750 --> 32:32.650
would you like to take a look?

32:35.830 --> 32:36.850
See if any one catches your eye.

32:38.220 --> 32:40.980
♪The regret of this life♪

32:41.300 --> 32:44.140
♪Shall be followed by reunion in the next♪

32:44.380 --> 32:49.780
♪Finding you is my only wish♪

33:14.540 --> 33:19.660
♪Twilight drifts through bustling streets♪

33:20.420 --> 33:25.580
♪Thick snow traps all the past in sheets♪

33:26.340 --> 33:32.260
♪Only with closed eyes, I see your face♪

33:32.460 --> 33:37.860
♪Red-rimmed eyes hide so many unsaid♪

33:38.300 --> 33:43.500
♪You're moonlight, frost that burns bright♪

33:44.340 --> 33:49.780
♪Shining through my fearful flight♪

33:50.380 --> 33:56.100
♪On tiptoe, I gaze at the hills at night♪

33:56.380 --> 34:00.380
♪Which lone lamp is lit just for my sight?♪

34:00.400 --> 34:01.810
A lifetime is filled

34:03.590 --> 34:04.810
with all eight kinds of suffering.

34:08.240 --> 34:09.570
But in this life of mine,

34:11.440 --> 34:12.820
I have only this one suffering.

34:14.800 --> 34:15.860
There is no cure for it

34:17.190 --> 34:18.690
and no one to resent for it.

34:20.540 --> 34:24.940
♪Let's stitch a gown from the moonlight...♪

34:24.960 --> 34:26.290
Perhaps before long,

34:27.550 --> 34:29.380
you too will follow in my footsteps.

34:31.230 --> 34:32.570
Don't.

34:34.150 --> 34:34.980
It's not worth it.

35:52.280 --> 35:54.420
The Dragon Deity's Power I granted you back then

35:54.590 --> 35:56.690
has long since merged with your souls.

35:58.000 --> 35:59.060
If you return it,

35:59.670 --> 36:01.500
you'll lose all your power.

36:02.110 --> 36:03.820
If returning it can seal Jiu Ying

36:03.880 --> 36:05.540
and save all living beings,

36:05.670 --> 36:07.250
we are willing to die.

36:08.480 --> 36:09.940
None of you needs to sacrifice yourselves.

36:10.510 --> 36:11.570
I have another way.

36:12.960 --> 36:14.380
You need only lend me

36:14.400 --> 36:15.420
your demon power.

36:16.070 --> 36:17.340
As for reclaiming my sacred power,

36:18.000 --> 36:18.980
I have other plans for that

36:19.550 --> 36:20.690
in the future.

36:35.230 --> 36:36.020
Bai Ze,

36:36.670 --> 36:37.570
Han Ba,

36:38.630 --> 36:39.610
Wu Zhiqi,

36:40.230 --> 36:41.170
and Xiaowei,

36:42.190 --> 36:44.250
I hope you will keep your promise

36:44.880 --> 36:45.820
and protect

36:45.960 --> 36:47.250
the Dragon Deity forever.

37:16.920 --> 37:18.340
Take him back to the Shilin Sect.

37:18.920 --> 37:19.380
Yes, Master.

37:43.000 --> 37:43.650
Ji Ling!

38:30.190 --> 38:30.860
Ji Ling?

38:31.510 --> 38:32.210
Ji Ling!

38:32.670 --> 38:33.420
Chi Wen!

38:58.190 --> 38:58.820
I'm saved!

38:59.880 --> 39:00.650
I'm going home!

39:00.760 --> 39:01.500
I've come to my senses!

39:02.110 --> 39:03.060
I'm going home!

39:03.230 --> 39:03.730
She's saved.

39:04.070 --> 39:05.340
My daughter is saved!

39:05.480 --> 39:06.380
Thank you, Dragon Deity!

39:06.880 --> 39:07.900
Thank you, Dragon Deity!

39:10.070 --> 39:11.020
Xiaowei

39:11.710 --> 39:13.540
was trapped by his own obsession.

39:14.440 --> 39:15.170
What about you?

39:15.510 --> 39:16.610
Do you have an obsession?

39:18.150 --> 39:19.090
I think

39:19.760 --> 39:22.060
an obsession is like the simplest

39:22.150 --> 39:23.460
and most complicated riddle in the world.

39:24.150 --> 39:25.570
I probably don't have one.

39:25.960 --> 39:27.540
At most, I just want

39:27.590 --> 39:29.730
to find the sweetest raspberry

39:29.960 --> 39:31.570
in a whole patch full of them.

39:33.150 --> 39:33.770
What about you,

39:34.070 --> 39:34.980
Master Dragon Deity?

39:35.920 --> 39:38.090
Obsession is like searching in endless darkness

39:39.070 --> 39:40.460
for a single night

39:42.710 --> 39:44.290
or searching in a boundless sea of suffering

39:45.760 --> 39:47.460
for a single drop of water untouched by bitterness.

40:16.880 --> 40:18.340
Chasing an obsession,

40:19.190 --> 40:20.650
worn down by the years,

40:21.590 --> 40:23.210
and trapped in a self-made prison...

40:28.400 --> 40:29.460
What a pity,

40:32.110 --> 40:33.130
Xiaowei.

40:48.140 --> 40:53.340
♪In the deep mountain abyss, the grieving mend sorrow and joy♪

40:54.100 --> 40:59.220
♪The River of Oblivion in their eyes, their hearts the Fountain of Youth♪

41:00.060 --> 41:05.820
♪Stitch by stitch, the cuckoo's bloodstained wish is sewn♪

41:06.100 --> 41:11.540
♪The wind blows, the clouds scatter, and tears fall on a jade plate♪

41:12.140 --> 41:14.820
♪Neither willing nor resentful♪

41:15.060 --> 41:17.900
♪Neither lacking nor whole♪

41:18.140 --> 41:20.540
♪Neither bright nor dark♪

41:20.660 --> 41:23.420
♪Neither speaking nor longing...♪

41:26.030 --> 41:27.340
Keeping a secret

41:28.670 --> 41:30.900
is like guarding a fragile candle flame.

41:32.630 --> 41:34.060
And so, you have no choice

41:34.400 --> 41:35.980
but to tell lie after lie.

41:58.070 --> 41:59.980
Don't you think the Dragon Deity and Ji Ling

42:00.920 --> 42:02.210
look a lot alike?

42:03.320 --> 42:04.020
Don't talk nonsense.

42:04.280 --> 42:05.510
Could Ji Ling be an illegitimate son?

42:05.510 --> 42:06.170
Nonsense!

42:06.630 --> 42:07.460
The nine dragon sons

42:07.880 --> 42:08.980
all have names and titles.

42:09.400 --> 42:10.540
How could there be an illegitimate son?

42:27.320 --> 42:28.380
Misses, need a boat?

42:30.230 --> 42:30.940
Watch your step.

42:47.590 --> 42:48.290
Oh, no.

43:05.230 --> 43:05.900
Master Chi Wen,

43:06.230 --> 43:07.540
the two stone beasts have been restored,

43:08.070 --> 43:09.290
but the barrier can't be reactivated

43:09.320 --> 43:10.610
without the Dragon Deity's Power.

43:12.630 --> 43:14.250
The barrier of the two stone beasts at the main gate

43:14.840 --> 43:16.420
only strips demons of their disguise.

43:17.400 --> 43:19.340
The Shilin Sect itself is covered in ancient formations

43:19.510 --> 43:21.420
powerful enough to destroy demons body and soul.

43:21.880 --> 43:22.690
There's no need to worry.

43:27.840 --> 43:29.250
I'm not worried about myself.

43:31.920 --> 43:33.090
What worries me

43:36.440 --> 43:37.500
is the Dragon Deity's Power

43:38.440 --> 43:39.690
still loose out there.

45:49.400 --> 45:50.610
You've crossed the line.

46:17.340 --> 46:22.780
♪Let's stitch a gown from the moonlight♪

46:23.060 --> 46:28.540
♪Stitch by stitch, the cuckoo's bloodstained wish is sewn♪

46:28.980 --> 46:34.900
♪The wind blows, the clouds scatter, and tears fall on a jade plate♪

46:35.260 --> 46:40.780
♪Neither willing nor resentful, neither lacking nor whole♪

46:41.180 --> 46:46.540
♪Neither bright nor dark, neither speaking nor longing♪

46:46.900 --> 46:52.620
♪The regret of this life shall be followed by reunion in the next♪

46:53.100 --> 46:58.660
♪Finding you is my only wish♪

47:17.220 --> 47:22.700
♪I close my eyes, and the years neither lessen nor grow♪

47:23.140 --> 47:28.860
♪Beside a sunken boat, dead trees wait for spring♪

47:29.340 --> 47:35.060
♪Some plant flowers, some burn joss paper♪

47:35.500 --> 47:41.940
♪In this mortal world, we've borrowed a hundred fleeting years♪

47:42.420 --> 47:48.620
♪Eyes red, walking on a road that never ends♪

47:49.060 --> 47:54.500
♪You are like moonlight, leading me back home♪

47:54.980 --> 48:00.220
♪By the little window, I leave a few lines of ink♪

48:00.700 --> 48:06.460
♪One line writes of withering yellow, one line of forgiveness♪

48:06.900 --> 48:13.420
♪Every word burns for you♪
